'''塔爾洪'''（{{lang-ka|ტარხუნა}}）是[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]的一種碳酸飲料<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3PM_FnWgPBAC&pg=PA43&lpg=PA43&dq=tarkhuna+georgian&source=bl&ots=u_crBaynjm&sig=pzsADhFkyE0FxPu63bDndK57axc&hl=en&ei=hKJnTZaLNcSGhQfQu-zxDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CDcQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=tarragon%20tarkhuna%20&f=false |title=The Georgian Feast by Darra Goldstein p.43, University of California Press, 1999 |access-date=2015-12-14 |archive-date=2014-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215053510/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3PM_FnWgPBAC&pg=PA43&lpg=PA43&dq=tarkhuna+georgian&source=bl&ots=u_crBaynjm&sig=pzsADhFkyE0FxPu63bDndK57axc&hl=en&ei=hKJnTZaLNcSGhQfQu-zxDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CDcQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=tarragon%20tarkhuna%20&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由龍蒿或香豬殃殃製成，顏色為綠色。塔爾洪發明於1887年，是由喬治亞的一位藥劑師研發的<ref>[http://www.lagidze.info/history Lagidze Waters] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518051555/http://www.lagidze.info/history |date=2015-05-18 }}</ref>。1981年，塔爾洪開始批量生產並普及至蘇聯全國。

